  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 1st level, you know when a demon, undead, monstruosity, aberration or sage creature is within 30ft of you, you know a inhuman entity is within this range, and a rough estimate how far it is, but not its exact location nor creature type. You identify the creature type of a inhuman once it enters your line of sight.</p><p>A creature under the effect of the <strong>Suppress Chakra</strong> Skill Action or under the effect of a sensory jutsu, feature or trait that would hide their presence (Such as the <em>Nondetection</em> jutsu) cannot be detected by this feature.</p>",
